text: @FedExHelp you are absolutely horrible. I sent a package for overnight on Thursday to a town 30 miles away and it’s still not there. These are concert tickets and you once again have screwed me over @FedEx you SUCK

@FedEx  i paid for a overnight package 30 miles north of me and you sent it on 2 planes and now it resides somewhere in a locked facility. You then charge for extras for your lateness? You are stealing money by way of false promises. You are the worst.
@KellyAnn1111 Hello Kelly, my name is Mary. Would you like my assistance today? Please DM your name, delivery address, tracking and phone number.

@FedExHelp I called CS and my overnight package is sitting in some facility and won’t go out until Monday. This has happened now 3 times on priority overnights. FedEx has lost their way... worst courier. And you charge consumers extra for this and I missed my deadline.
